reviewText:
If you are familiar with Central Asian, or specifically Uzbek music, I recommend this singer. He has very nice voice. This DVD is one of Ozodbek's annual concerts that held in Tashkent. You can preview one of his song (called "Eshigingda" ("At your door") from this concert  here: [...]
 I highly recommend this DVD for those who are interested in Central Asian and Uzbekistan's music.
